OL,3,CDoncaster man jailed for 'sustained
OL,4,Cand violent' hammer attack
OL,6,FA man from Doncaster has been jailed
OL,7,Ffollowing a violent hammer attack.
OL,9,FDouglas Thomson armed himself with the
OL,10,Fhammer before striking the woman to
OL,11,Fthe back of the head during the
OL,12,Fassault in March 2024.
OL,14,FAfter knocking her over, Thomson then
OL,15,Fclimbed on top of her and continued to
OL,16,Fattack her with the hammer before
OL,17,Fpressing down on her throat and eyes.
