OL,6,FTwo witnesses were able to guide
OL,7,FThomson into another room and
OL,8,Fbarricade him in there until officers
OL,9,Farrived moments later.
OL,11,FThe victim was rushed to hospital with
OL,12,Fserious injuries. Thomson, 60,
OL,13,Freceived hospital treatment for a self-
OL,14,Finflicted stab wound.
OL,16,FThomson, of Wellington Road in
OL,17,FLindholme, was subsequently charged
OL,18,Fwith attempted murder and pleaded not
OL,19,Fguilty in court.
