OL,6,FA jury found Thomson guilty last
OL,7,Fmonth. He was jailed for 19 years in a
OL,8,Fsentencing hearing at Sheffield Crown
OL,9,FCourt on Friday 24 October.
OL,11,FDetective Constable Alexandra Owen was
OL,12,Fthe officer in charge of this case.
OL,14,FShe said: "This was a sustained and
OL,15,Fviolent attack which left the victim
OL,16,Fwith not only horrific physical
OL,17,Finjuries but a long-lasting
OL,18,Fpsychological impact.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/5
