OL,6,F"There is absolutely no justification
OL,7,Ffor this kind of violence and I am
OL,8,Fpleased a lengthy custodial sentence
OL,9,Fhas been served.
OL,11,F"I would like to thank the officers
OL,12,Fand staff involved in this case from
OL,13,Fthose involved in Thomson's arrest and
OL,14,Fthe evidence gathering at the scene to
OL,15,Fthose who have worked diligently to
OL,16,Fsecure a charge, conviction and
OL,17,Fsentence in court.
