OL,6,F"I would also like to thank the three
OL,7,Fwitnesses to the incident who
OL,8,Fundoubtedly played a pivotal role in
OL,9,Freducing the risk of harm to others in
OL,10,Fwhat must have been an incredibly
OL,11,Ftraumatic set of circumstances.
OL,13,F"They will be presented with the High
OL,14,FSheriff's Award for their immense
OL,15,Fcourage, bravery and strength of
OL,16,Fcharacter and it is no less than they
OL,17,Fdeserve."
